- subt_example_node can be launched individually with roslaunch subt_example example_robot.launch name:=<robot name>
- Also migrating teleop_twist_keyboard with detection for robots that it can control

message.raw:
Fix install of artifact.pb.h header

This header needs to be installed for an extending catkin workspace to
use it (necessary to generate score reports).

message.raw:
Add beacon interval to comms client and fix bug

Adds a timer-based beacon broadcast functionality to the communication
client. Also fixes an outstanding bug where repeated uses of the
Bind(...) function do not succeed (Issue #51).
